			<h2 class="excerpt-title"><a href="https://tasteofmaroc.com/moroccan-henna-styles-and-traditions/" class="excerpt-link">Moroccan Henna Styles and Traditions</a></h2>
			<div class="excerpt-excerpt">
				<p>Henna tattoos are a traditional way that Moroccan women beautify their hands and feet, particularly for special occasions and celebrations. Whether simple or intricate, Moroccan henna designs and styles can vary from one part of the country to another.</p>
